Installs Required Libraries
diffusers, transformers, torch, torchvision, matplotlib, etc.

Imports Necessary Modules
PyTorch
Stable Diffusion pipeline from Hugging Face
Image processing and visualization libraries

Sets Device
Uses GPU (CUDA) if available, otherwise CPU.

Loads a Pretrained Model
Loads the Stable Diffusion Turbo model (stabilityai/sd-turbo)
Disables the safety checker
Moves model to selected device

Defines Prompts
Medical text prompts related to:
Healthy chest X-rays
Pneumonia
Ground-glass opacities
These prompts are used to generate synthetic medical images.

Generates Synthetic Images
Creates 512Ã—512 images
Saves them in a folder named:

synthetic_image_dataset

Displays Generated Images
Uses Matplotlib to show generated X-ray images in a grid format.
